JD 9:

You have:

• Conduct market research & trend analysis to identify sourcing opportunities
• Generate solicitations, evaluate proposals, and negotiate contract terms
• Monitor vendor commercial performance and ensure compliance
• Present sourcing outcomes to procurement committees
Knowledge of international procurement practices and public/private sector procedures.
