Knowledge of sustainable procurement trends and practices, including supplier diversity and inclusion activities.
Project Management skills with extensive experience in managing multiple related projects.
Ability to deal sensitively in a multicultural environment and build effective working relationships.
Proficiency in MS Office applications and knowledge of systems relevant to the functional area.
Superior communication skills in English (verbal, written, and comprehension).
Other language skills would be an asset.

